Changes between 3.0.0 and 3.0.1:
 + added search module
 + added possibility to edit machine's domain name
 + added security checking when downloading an attachment
 + added additional user selectable themes
 * fixed wrongly selected machine's aquired date
 * fixed page redirection mechanism
 * fixed log and history views to work with multiple server versions
 * fixed session expiration
 * fixed/workaround 30 cookie limit in Opera browser
